Samit is taking a long time to get the wheels turning in his innings and after tapping that ball into the off side, did take a few steps down the pitch before ball-watching got the better of him. Short ball on fourth stump, Rizwan tries for another front foot pull but picks out Haris Rauf at deep square leg jogging in from the rope and takes a simple catch 10 yards in at waist height.
